<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Mentor Invitation - Kindora</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
      }
      .header img {
        max-width: 150px;
        height: auto;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #5764f2;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #5764f2;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      {{#if logoUrl}}
      <div class="header">
        <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Kindora" />
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <h1>You're Invited to be a Mentor!</h1>
      <p>
        {{organizationName}} has invited you to join their team as a mentor. This is an exciting opportunity to share your expertise and make a difference in the community.
      </p>

      <p>
        As a mentor, you'll have access to the organization's dashboard where you can:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Guide and support volunteers</li>
        <li>Share your knowledge and experience</li>
        <li>Help shape the organization's initiatives</li>
        <li>Connect with other mentors and volunteers</li>
      </ul>

      <a href="{{baseUrl}}/accept-mentor-invitation?token={{token}}" class="button">Accept Invitation</a>

      <p>
        If you did not expect this invitation or believe it was sent to you in error, you can safely ignore this email.<br />
        For security reasons, this link will expire in 24 hours.
      </p>

      <p>Thank you,<br />The Kindora Team</p>

      <p>
        Need help? Our team is always ready to support you.
        <a href="{{supportUrl}}" style="color: #5764f2; text-decoration: none"
          >Contact us!</a
        >
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Copyright &copy; 2025 Kindora. Kindora connects volunteers with opportunities to make a difference in their community.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
